# NativeWind Styling

- Ensure NativeWind setup files are in place (`global.css`, Babel/Metro config, env types).
- Prefer token classes over hard-coded colors.
- Use simple conditional className patterns; extract variable when logic grows.
- Use `StyleSheet` or animated style objects for complex dynamic/animated styles.
